[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0139","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0139.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0473","title":"Rsync rsync 目录权限非预期修改漏洞","description":"rsync 2.3.1 之前版本存在权限处理缺陷，在文件传输过程中服务端目录权限可能被错误地应用到客户端工作目录。攻击者可通过构造特定权限的共享目录，诱使客户端执行 rsync 同步操作后，导致客户端工作目录的权限被非预期修改，可能造成信息泄露或权限提升。该漏洞影响广泛使用的 rsync 工具各早期版本，建议升级至 2.3.1 及以上版本修复。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0473"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.367","remediation":"升级 rsync 至 2.3.1 或更高版本，该版本修复了同步过程中权限被意外修改的问题。如无法升级，避免在不受信任的目录上执行 rsync 拉取操作，并在传输后手动检查并重置工作目录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/145"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0139.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0138","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0138.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0472","title":"NetApp C630 Netcache SNMP 默认团体名安全绕过漏洞","description":"NetApp C630 Netcache 设备存在安全绕过漏洞，管理员尝试禁用 SNMP 默认社区字符串 \"public\" 时未能成功移除，导致该默认配置仍可被利用。远程攻击者可通过 SNMP 协议使用 \"public\" 社区字符串查询设备信息，获取敏感配置数据，绕过访问控制机制。该漏洞影响 NetApp C630 Netcache 设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0472"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.237","remediation":"立即彻底禁用 NetApp C630 Netcache 上的 SNMP v1/v2c 服务（执行 `snmpset disable` 命令或通过 Web 管理界面关闭 SNMP）。如业务必须使用 SNMP 监控，建议升级至 SNMPv3 并配置用户认证（auth/priv），避免使用明文团体字符串。同时，在网络边界和交换机 ACL 中限制仅允许信任的管理主机访问设备的 UDP 161 端口。该设备已停止维护，无法通过补丁修复此漏洞，最彻底的方案是迁移至受支持的替代产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0472","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-240","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-240/"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0138.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1021","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1021.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1245","title":"UCD-SNMP SNMP 服务器信息泄露漏洞","description":"ucd-snmp SNMP 服务器 3.52 版本的 vacm 模块未能正确禁用对默认 public 团体字符串的访问权限，导致远程未认证攻击者可通过 SNMP 协议查询目标系统上的敏感系统信息，如系统配置、网络接口状态及运行进程等。该漏洞影响 ucd-snmp 3.52 版本，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1245"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.670","remediation":"升级 ucd-snmp 至 4.0.0 及以上版本，或迁移至 Net-SNMP 5.x。同时修改 SNMP 默认 community 字符串，替换 \"public\"/\"private\" 为强密码，并配置 SNMPv3 使用加密认证。在防火墙层面限制 SNMP (UDP 161/162) 仅允许可信管理源 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2086","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1245.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1245","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1245.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1245.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fpj3-2577-2q59/GHSA-fpj3-2577-2q59.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1245.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000598.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e2ff807e9fd18d30d388cc2c559c111ff993a143/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1021.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0142","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0142.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0475","title":"Procmail .procmailrc 条件竞争任意文件读取漏洞","description":"procmail 在处理 .procmailrc 文件时存在条件竞争漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞读取目标系统上运行 procmail 用户权限可访问的任意文件。该漏洞源于 .procmailrc 文件在处理过程中的检查与使用之间存在时间窗口，攻击者可通过符号链接攻击等方式利用此时间差绕过访问控制，实现任意文件读取。此漏洞影响 procmail 各版本，攻击者需具备本地账户权限，利用条件较低但危害较大，可导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0475"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.627","remediation":"升级 procmail 至 3.12 或更高版本，该版本修复了 .procmailrc 处理过程中的条件竞争漏洞。procmail 已停止维护，建议迁移至 maildrop 作为替代方案。无法升级时，限制 procmail 可执行文件的属组权限，仅允许受信任用户执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0475"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0142.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0140","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0140.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0474","title":"ICQ ICQ Webserver 目录遍历漏洞","description":"ICQ Webserver 存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 URL 中构造 `../` 序列绕过路径限制，访问用户个人目录之外的任意文件，导致系统敏感信息泄露。攻击无需认证，利用方式简单，对服务器文件保密性造成严重威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0474"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.487","remediation":"升级 ICQ 至 99a 或更高版本以修复路径遍历漏洞；在 ICQ 设置中禁用内置 Web 服务器功能（默认监听 2000 端口）；在防火墙策略中阻止外部对 TCP 2000 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。如不再使用 ICQ，建议完全卸载以避免历史遗留漏洞暴露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0474"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0140.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0112","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0112.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0439","title":"procmail 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"procmail 邮件处理工具 3.12 之前版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于在处理 procmailrc 配置文件中的宏扩展时未正确校验边界，远程或本地攻击者可通过构造恶意的配置文件触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。此漏洞影响运行 openlinux 及其他使用受影响 procmail 版本的系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0439"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.947","remediation":"升级 procmail 至 3.12 或更高版本，该版本修复了配置文件扩展中的缓冲区溢出问题。对于老旧系统无法升级的，可在 procmailrc 中禁用危险宏扩展，并限制仅信任用户可修改配置文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0439"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0112.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0721","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0721.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0921","title":"BMC Patrol Agent 3.2.5 UDP Flooding 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BMC Patrol Agent 3.2.5 存在 UDP 泛洪拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 UDP 端口发送大量恶意数据包，导致服务资源耗尽而无法正常响应合法请求。该漏洞影响 BMC Patrol Agent 3.2.5 版本，攻击条件简单，仅需构造持续 UDP 流量即可触发拒绝服务状态。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0921"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.013","remediation":"建议升级 BMC Patrol Agent 至 3.3.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 UDP 端口处理漏洞。如无法升级，可在防火墙配置规则限制对 Patrol Agent UDP 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接，并启用流量速率限制以缓解 UDP 泛洪攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/4291.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13204","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1879"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0721.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0183","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0183.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0610","title":"Webcart CGI 程序信息泄露漏洞","description":"Webcart CGI 程序存在配置不当漏洞，攻击者可利用不安全的访问控制直接获取 Webcart 购物车系统中的敏感信息，包括用户订单详情、联系信息等。该漏洞影响使用 Webcart CGI 的早期电子商务网站，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程访问，属于信息泄露类安全缺陷。建议修改 CGI 脚本权限配置并实施访问控制。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0610"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.933","remediation":"立即检查服务器上是否仍在运行 Webcart CGI 程序，若无需使用则彻底删除或禁用该 CGI 脚本。如业务必须保留，应限制 CGI 目录权限为仅可执行必要文件，配置 Web 服务器（如 Apache）通过 .htaccess 或 location 指令限制可访问 IP 范围，并禁用目录列表与符号链接跟随。同时建议迁移至现代受支持的电商平台，避免使用已停止维护的 CGI 程序暴露敏感信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0610","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0610.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/webcart.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--99fbdaa8-4c6c-4442-9bb2-6a51e40a9543.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0183.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0183.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0182","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0182.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0609","title":"SoftCart SoftCart.exe CGI 配置不当信息泄露漏洞","description":"SoftCart 电子商务软件的 CGI 程序 SoftCart.exe 存在错误配置漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HTTP 请求利用该配置缺陷，获取服务器上的敏感信息（如订单数据、客户信息等）。该漏洞影响使用 SoftCart CGI 程序的 Web 服务器，CVE 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议升级软件版本或限制 CGI 脚本访问权限进行修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0609"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.817","remediation":"将 SoftCart 订单数据存储目录移出 Web 根目录（如移至 /var/softcart/data），通过 Apache 的 <Directory> 指令或 .htaccess 的 Deny from all 禁止直接访问该目录；将文件权限设置为 600，仅允许 Web 进程用户读取。由于 SoftCart 已停止维护，建议迁移至支持敏感数据加密存储的受支持购物车系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0609","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0609.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2055/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c26f55c1-1cb8-453a-ae44-fe71d70ff34b.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/InfoSecWarrior/Vulnerable-Box-Resources/blob/c784bcf63e1ec5c3a0116043d8653d00f0a21a0b/Vulnhub/OZ/oz-1-nikto-8080-output.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0182.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0180","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0180.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0608","title":"PDG Shopping Cart 信息泄露漏洞","description":"PDG Shopping Cart 的 CGI 程序 shopper.cgi 存在配置不当漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用错误的访问控制配置直接访问未授权的敏感信息。该漏洞影响使用了 PDG Shopping Cart 的早期 Web 服务器，攻击者无需身份认证即可窃取用户订单数据、购物车内容等隐私信息。厂商未提供官方修复补丁，建议升级至更安全的购物车系统或移除不必要的 CGI 脚本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0608"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.690","remediation":"立即移除或替换已停止维护的 PDG Shopping Cart，升级至现代受支持的购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce）。若无法立即替换，在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）配置中对 shopper.cgi 添加 IP 白名单访问控制，并移除 CGI 目录的目录浏览权限，防止未授权访问泄露敏感信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","http://www.pdgsoft.com/Security/security.html.","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3857","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0608","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0608.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jwx2-gr93-39wv/GHSA-jwx2-gr93-39wv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0180.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0180.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0176","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0176.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0605","title":"Order Form 1.0 购物车 CGI 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Order Form 1.0 在线购物车 CGI 程序存在配置不当漏洞，远程攻击者可通过直接访问该 CGI 脚本的特定配置文件或未授权的 URL 路径，获取购物车系统中存储的客户订单信息、交易记录等私密数据。该漏洞属于信息泄露类型，攻击条件简单，无需认证即可利用，影响使用该购物车程序的 Web 站点。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0605"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.337","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器上移除或禁用 `order_form.cgi` 脚本。修改 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）配置文件，限制对 CGI 目录的访问权限，添加 IP 白名单或 HTTP 认证。如仍需购物车功能，应升级至支持安全配置的现代购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce 等），并确保 CGI 脚本不以全局可读权限运行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0605","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0605.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vhcv-cv27-25rw/GHSA-vhcv-cv27-25rw.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2021/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0176.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0176.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0176.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0168","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0168.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0443","title":"BMC Patrol 管理软件远程重放攻击漏洞","description":"BMC Patrol 管理软件存在认证会话重放漏洞，远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探捕获管理员与 Patrol Agent 之间的认证报文，无需任何身份凭证即可重放截获的认证数据包，从而获取管理员密码并完全控制 Patrol Agent 服务。该漏洞影响多个 Patrol 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议升级到最新版本或启用加密通信以防止中间人攻击。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0443"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.467","remediation":"升级 BMC Patrol Agent 至包含身份认证重放防护的最新版本，禁用旧版不安全的身份认证协议。启用 SSL/TLS 加密通信以保护 Patrol 管理流量不被嗅探。在网络层面限制管理端口（通常为 TCP 6767/6768）仅允许受信任管理主机访问。如无法升级，建议在网络边界部署 IPS 规则检测认证请求重放特征作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13204"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0168.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0153","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0153.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0480","title":"GNU Midnight Commander 符号链接攻击拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Midnight Commander 4.x 版本存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在当前目录下创建恶意符号链接，诱使 Midnight Commander 在处理文件列表时错误地跟随该链接，导致程序崩溃或资源耗尽，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Midnight Commander 4.x 系列版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，利用前提是攻击者拥有本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0480"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:29.260","remediation":"升级 Midnight Commander 至 4.5.50 及以上版本，该版本修复了符号链接竞争条件问题。如无法升级，可通过 `mc --no-subshell` 启动以降低攻击面，并避免在不可信目录中使用 MC 的文件管理功能。在系统层面，可将 `/tmp` 挂载为 `noexec`、`nodev`、`nosuid` 以限制本地攻击者的提权路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0480"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0153.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0133","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0133.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0469","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 窗口欺骗漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 存在窗口欺骗漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造特制的恶意网页，利用浏览器窗口地址栏与内容区域显示不一致的缺陷，在地址栏显示合法网站的 URL，而实际内容区域加载攻击者控制的恶意页面，从而诱骗用户输入敏感信息（如密码、信用卡号等）。该漏洞无需任何用户交互即可触发，攻击者通过电子邮件链接或嵌入恶意网页的第三方网站进行钓鱼攻击。影响运行 IE 5.0 的 Windows 系统，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0469"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.857","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 Internet Explorer 5.0 的窗口欺骗行为中，攻击者可伪造合法网站窃取用户信息。建议立即升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 2 或更高版本以消除该漏洞；鉴于 Internet Explorer 已于 2022 年 6 月终止支持，强烈建议迁移至 Microsoft Edge（Chromium 内核）浏览器，并启用 SmartScreen 筛选器和窗口安全策略防止类似欺骗攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0469"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0133.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0128","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0128.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0467","title":"Webcom CGI Guestbook 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Webcom CGI Guestbook 中的 wguest.exe 及 rguest.exe 程序存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向 template 参数传入恶意文件路径（如包含 ../ 的路径遍历字符串），绕过程序对输入参数的过滤检查，读取目标服务器上的任意文件（如 /etc/passwd、配置文件等）。该漏洞影响 WebCom datakommunikation Guestbook 0.1 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。成功利用可导致系统敏感信息泄露，为后续攻击提供铺垫。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0467"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.433","remediation":"立即删除或替换 Webcom CGI Guestbook 程序 wguest.exe 和 rguest.exe，该软件已停止维护且无安全更新。建议迁移至现代 Guestbook 方案，同时在 Web 服务器层面禁用 CGI 脚本对任意文件路径的 template 参数传递，配置 URL 重写规则拦截类似请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0467","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20446"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0128.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0128.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0128.toml"}]